import {Component, OnInit} from '@angular/core'; import {AuthServiceService} from "../services/auth-service.service"; @Component({ selector: 'app-sidebar', templateUrl: './sidebar.component.html', styleUrls: ['./sidebar.component.css'] }) export class SidebarComponent implements OnInit { admin:boolean = false; constructor(private auth:AuthServiceService ) { } ngOnInit(): void { this.admin = this.auth.isAuthenticatedAsAdmin(); } isAuthenticated(){ console.log("isAuthenticated"); return this.auth.isAuthenticated(); } isAuthenticatedAsAdmin(){ console.log("isAuthenticatedAsAdmin"); return this.admin; } doLogout(){ console.log("click"); this.auth.logout(); } printUser(){ console.log("STAMPO ADMIN: " + this.auth.isAuthenticatedAsAdmin()); } }
